{"tid":2018231,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"洗衫應該用邊隻梳打粉","createTime":"2020-05-15T13:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T13:19:07.000Z","uid":295532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"833cfbc3aa0caca5115ee6aed7e4530bb7f2c773","tid":2018231,"uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:18:12.000Z","msg":"呢排洗冬天衫，想洗乾淨啲tg殘留物，過往用開呢隻溝洗衣粉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T4oB6FE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT4oB6FE.jpg&h=d12360cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時會想用梳打粉去清油漬，見超級市場有賣呢隻，寫明去油污<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1PVH2ep.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1PVH2ep.jpg&h=03822653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩隻成粉唔一樣，效果唔同，上網睇到有啲亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n洗衫去tg殘留物嘅就用第一隻，去油污用第二隻，我係咪可以咁理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d29294d08d175a57e6312d9246e8257c40b2b89","tid":2018231,"uid":247719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}